casebody.data:
Charles L. RYAN, Director, Arizona Department of Corrections, petitioner,
v.
David Scott DETRICH. No. 13-868. Supreme Court of the United States May 27, 2014.

Case below, 740 F.3d 1237 .

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.
